Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.03,0:01:03.46,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但是却
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.68,0:01:08.98,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}总有一天愿望会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:12.67,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但是「总有一天」是哪一天
