Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.74,0:02:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  原来是小鸠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪尾吕义先生  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在和大家一起去郊游
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.59,0:02:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你怎么一脸高兴的样子  原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  非常高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以猪尾吕义先生也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么  你来接啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是花户小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞错了  是艾草托儿所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在这里帮忙的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺精神的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:03:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花呢  你把电话给她听一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个…我们现在正要去郊游
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有事啊  你能帮我转达吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把托儿所关了  然后给我滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还债时间不能再拖了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是追债先生吗  前段时间来托儿所欺负大家的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来那些家伙做了这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是你做的  我却责怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个有趣的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.31,0:03:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不好意思  帮忙就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要毁了托儿所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  你要好好转达给清花哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要毁了托儿所…刚才那个人应该是和清花老师认识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去郊游了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？猪尾吕义先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来之后睡个午觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要别人等你多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都因为你  出发时间都推迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…追债先生是清花老师认识的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才打来电话…是一位男性打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说要毁了托儿所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话的事不要对清花老师说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？但是但是…总觉得那是个很可怕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  不许说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠  藤本  要出发了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:06:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是一如既往把入口设在奇怪的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊的年轮蛋糕店
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  原来是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你这店名也太直白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊  不只是职业  连店名都是被规定的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙连这个都要规定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫他「那家伙」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你变成这副样子还没吸取教训吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有吸取教训的理由  我又没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惹了那么大的麻烦  还敢这么说  你这呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的话要是被他听到了  那可就不是布娃娃这么简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好会变成拇指人偶大小的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个话题到此结束  你今天来这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么  别装模作样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事想调查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐吧  姑且听你说说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池塘  好大的池塘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁了托儿所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上打电话的人是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠  俊彦  满里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该吃便当了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞到额头了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠从早上起就总是撞得疼疼的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得你有点发呆  有什么心事吗  小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发呆是家常便饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是家常便饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要给清花老师添多余的担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  你想要这个艾草托儿所的现状和相关人员的情报是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  一副没出息的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那引以为豪的情报收集能力废掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我来  你的样子要没出息几万倍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.74,0:09:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  没想到你会说出这种话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是以前的你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说句「给我去调查」  就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不听你的  你就会吐火加拳头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就如你所愿  给你个特大号的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  烤好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙对这份工作相当熟练了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这副样子要是被你以前的小弟看到  他们肯定会哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被你这布娃娃说教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的事  我会帮你查查的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那个女孩有关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就看在你求我的份上…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}这个真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋怎么自己随便吃起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满里奈  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠有什么心事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？啊…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…完全没有  是真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  满里奈在做一件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到的话  就会变得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠  满里奈  我们来玩捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪子布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:10:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠是鬼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  小鸠鸠数数的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家会躲起来  你要好好找哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  小鸠会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.11,0:11:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土产就给这点儿啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在上面叠上几十个个我也拿得动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  可恶  这个身体真是麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:11:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还更没出息了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被你这家伙说教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见啊  银生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.89,0:12:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一副落魄的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使外表变了  本质也没有改变么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回去吗  异世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小丫头么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对小鸠出手的话我就勒死你  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会和你做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.99,0:13:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都躲到哪儿去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  小鸠很开心的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人都还没找到哦  小鸠鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又去找奇怪的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来会拖很久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很会躲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  因为我现在是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼要把藏起来的人找出来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.78,0:14:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是已经到时间了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  要回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠…没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到俊彦和卓哉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被找到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到让和由香里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义男也找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里也有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那里也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那里也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠头上还粘着树叶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真笨呢  我帮你拿下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后来照一张纪念照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 满里奈不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师请和大家待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去找
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  还躲在什么地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.20,0:16:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是能早点找到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.35,0:16:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那边找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满里奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.87,0:17:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  没找到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说捉迷藏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是四片叶子的苜蓿草
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到的话呢  就会变得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:17:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想送给小鸠鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小鸠鸠今天好像没什么精神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然到处都找过了还是没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.64,0:18:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.28,0:18:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为满里奈帮我寻找幸福  就打起精神来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风景也不错  就在这里照相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  大家别动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和老师  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:18:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没关系  看前面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.22,0:19:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四片叶子的苜蓿草
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  小鸠鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠  快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.45,0:19:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  有好多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了好多好多的幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  再来照一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.09,0:19:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  年轮蛋糕变得破破烂烂了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得玄琥大人给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊  一个接一个的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是熊叔那里的小弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.23,0:20:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.07,0:20:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  是瑞祥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有玄琥大人的传话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说「委托的事情已经调查完了」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个模样也想装酷酷地笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么你这混鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:21:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪尾吕义先生没回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…猪尾吕义先生不会因为太小了被夹在什么地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.63,0:21:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者掉在路边的排水沟里…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是被压住了什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.40,0:21:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  猪尾吕义先生陷入大危机了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.58,0:21:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁陷入危机了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗  是年轮蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  郊游怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.39,0:21:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有礼物给猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.38,0:21:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幸福的苜蓿草
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点被压过了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪尾吕义先生的幸福我也找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.82,0:21:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家都能够永远幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.07,0:22:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾草托儿所的大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.12,0:22:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于艾草托儿所  前任园长似乎因为被骗而借了很多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前任园长？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.13,0:22:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是冲蒲清花的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.29,0:22:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两年前去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.49,0:22:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗他的是一群相当糟糕的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.42,0:22:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且似乎冲蒲清花的亲人也牵涉其中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.01,0:22:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还真是麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.03,0:22:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.79,0:22:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾草托儿所迟早会被压垮么
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------NEXT-------------------
